nodes.text: Unidentified Wroonian defense force starfighter squadron

During the Galactic Civil War, this starfighter squadron served with the Wroonian defense force, and counted T'Charek Haathi among its members. The squadron eventually went rogue, and began attacking Imperial corporate shipping, drawing the attention of the Imperial Navy. The squadron was decimated in a reprisal attack, although Haathi survived and escaped to the mining colony on Rodaj.
